N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 86.7 - Wine lists

State Regulations
A manufacturer or wholesaler may furnish, give, rent, loan or sell wine lists or wine menus to retail on-premises licensees. The wine
lists or wine menus may contain the name of the retail
licensee. Notes
